slipped back three and WMC ended three cents firmer.
</P>
<P>
All the major banks made gains, with NAB rising 14.3 cents,
Westpac gaining six, ANZ two higher and CBA adding one cent.
</P>
<P>
The gold index ended 24 points better at 1351.3 and in Sydney
the metal was trading 3.15 stronger at 334.05 U.S. dollars.
