It's a great achievement for the country's ready-made garment
sector, for our next generation," he told a press conference
Sunday.
</P>
<P>
The BGMEA chief revealed that foreign buyers welcomed the
opposition decision and were planning to place big orders for the
next season.
</P>
<P>
Given the political stability in the country, the garment
sector would be able to fetch 5 billion dollars in export income,
up from 3.1 billion in the 196-97 fiscal, he claimed. 
