<TEXT>
<P>
SEOUL, October 6 (Xinhua) -- Foreign direct investment in South
Korea totaled 4.463 billion U.S. dollars in the first half of this
year, rising from 3.2 billion dollars for the whole of last year.
</P>
<P>
