Liberation Tigers of Tamil Eelam (LTTE) rebels starting on May 12,
has resulted in heavy casualties on both sides, the sources said.
</P>
<P>
The LTTE has been fighting an ethnic war for a separate state
of their own in the north and east of the country for 14 years.
