be adjusted before the United States businessmen invest more in
the country.
</P>
<P>
So far, U.S. investment in Romania amounted to 200 million
U.S. dollars. Ciorbea hoped that the figure would rise to 3
billion dollars by the end of the century.
</P>
<P>
Grossman arrived here Sunday on a two-day official visit.
