went off in a Tel Aiv bus Sunday night, but causing no casualties.
</P>
<P>
Tel Aviv police spokeswoman Linda Menuhin said the man aroused
the driver's suspicion when he boarded the bus on a busy highway
in northern Tel Aviv. When the driver began questioning him, he
fled after placing the small bomb in the bus trash bin.
